This website presents internal results from data analysis of the Influenzanet central database integrating individual data and aggregated data from participating countries.
Its content is built on a daily basis.

Please do not share this website into public documents, it is dedicated to show internal results and process.

The code for the analysis and this website is available at [https://github.com/influenzanet/data-analysis-europe](https://github.com/influenzanet/data-analysis-europe)
